            <li><em>Shop Class as Soulcraft</em> by Matthew B. Crawford. I'm only a few chapters in, but every sentence is a banger so far.</li>
            <li>All the <em>Red Dwarf</em> novelisations by Rob Grant & Doug Naylor. I have mixed feelings which I really must go into more detail about at some point.</li>
            <li>Some fantastic blogs by fellow devs like <a href="https://danaciocan.com/" target="_blank">Dana Ciocan</a> and <a href="https://mattandrews.info/" target="_blank">Matt Andrews</a> (both former colleagues!).</li>
        </ul>
